== Deaths == * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|Tenshō|qq=|qq=draft}} 4th year ([[Julian calendar]] [[1576]] [[December 15]]) – Kitabatake Tomonori, the 8th head of the Kitabatake family and governor of Ise (born [[1528]]). * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|Kan'ei|qq=|qq=draft}} 19th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] [[1643]] [[January 15]]) – Tachibana Muneshige, lord of the Tanakura Domain and the Yanagawa Domain (born [[1567]] or [[1569]]). * [[Hōreki]] 4th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] [[1755]] [[January 7]]) – Nabeshima Muneshige, lord of the Saga Domain (born [[1687]]).
